      "title": "IOC restricts fuel distribution",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Manoj Gupta, Managing Director of Ceylon Indian Oil Company (LIOC) says that fuel will not be distributed to the filling stations from today (8) to the 10th and the fuel distribution to the filling stations will resume from the 11th.",
        "Mr. Manoj Gupta further mentioned that fuel will be released only to Ceylon Petroleum Corporation and industries during that period."
      ],
